Starting a web agency has been on my mind for years. In 2025, I finally made the leap and launched **NC Digital** — a South Wales-based studio focused on building fast, functional websites that help real businesses grow.

This isn't just about code or design — it's about creating websites that make a difference for the people behind the business.

#### Where It All Started

After nearly a decade working in web development for agencies and businesses, I saw what worked — and what didn't. Too many clients were overpaying for underperforming sites. So I started something leaner, faster, and more honest.

#### Why NC Digital Exists

I built NC Digital to support:

- Tradespeople who want a reliable, mobile-ready site
- Startups who need a fast launch without the drama
- Small businesses who want to grow through digital

We focus on clean designs, smart structure, SEO-friendly foundations, and full WordPress access — so you're always in control.

#### What We Do

At NC Digital, we specialise in custom WordPress websites, built to perform across all devices. From small brochure sites to SEO-friendly service pages, everything we build is made to help you grow — not just look good.

#### Why WordPress

We work with WordPress because it gives our clients full control, flexibility, and scalability — plus, it's great for SEO and content updates. It powers more than 40% of all websites globally. [Learn more about WordPress](https://wordpress.org).

#### What Makes Us Different

We're a small team, and that's by design. No layers of account managers, no slow turnarounds — just honest advice and properly built websites that work. We treat every client like a partner, not a transaction.

#### What's Next

NC Digital is just getting started, but our goal is simple: help as many businesses in South Wales and beyond get online with confidence. This blog will share our builds, tips on web strategy, SEO, and more along the way. We follow industry best practices including guidance from [Google's SEO Starter Guide](https://developers.google.com/search/docs/fundamentals/seo-starter-guide) to keep every build clean and crawlable.

#### Ready to Work Together?

We offer sites starting from **£400** and monthly maintenance packages if you need help growing your site over time.

[Get a free website plan](/free-website-plan)
